ou know for Christmas and - and she says, I don't see why we can't have a party? She said, certainly Jessie, you - you remember that? She said, certainly have a party, ask some of your friends and just tell me how many are coming, and - we'll cater for it
. So I asked my father and an uncle, and - Mr.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8941568\charrsid2967080  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7146469\charrsid2967080 S. and I remember - Walter Young was there. Mrs.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
