\insrsid8941568\charrsid2967080 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7146469\charrsid2967080 ner. Aye. Aye. And a lad I was going with at that time Alec}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8941568\charrsid2967080  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
